<br>
Anyone else find this to be true? And if so, shouldnt exp in a group be faster? Im not asking for a nerf on solo'ing, just hoping maybe we can get a bigger exp bonus possibly for grouping and hunting for AA points<br>
<br>
Comments?<br>
